Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:34.43,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}It is the year 2009.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.18,0:01:39.35,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}The alien spacecraft that fell\Nto Earth 10 years before{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:42.45,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}has been reborn as the\Ngigantic battleship "Macross."{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:47.39,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}However, on the day that the Macross\Nwas scheduled to be launched,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:51.19,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}its automatic defense system of alien\Norigin suddenly activated itself,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:56.32,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}firing the main cannon and destroying\Nan unidentified warship.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:58.62,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Humanity was plunged into\Nunavoidable conflict.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.69,0:02:01.74,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Meanwhile, air-racer Hikaru Ichijo,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:03.88,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}a pilot invited to the launch ceremony\Nby Major Roy Focker,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:05.89,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}was accidentally ordered to fly\Na Valkyrie fighter{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:10.96,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}by 1st Lt. Misa Hayase, a Macross\Ndefense systems operator.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:14.38,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}However, overwhelmed by his\Nfirst taste of combat,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:19.82,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Hikaru was shot down by beams\Nfired from an enemy pod.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:28.25,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}As the alien forces begin their ground\Ndescent, the fighting enters a brief lull.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Twenty-four unidentified objects are\Ncurrently on a descent course.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}You weren't able to detect them until now?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}No, sir.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Radar is useless due to the use of reaction\Nweaponry during the first attack wave.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}So the first wave was a decoy. Whoever\Nthey are, they're good.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Hayase, can't you recall\NMajor Focker?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}No, sir. He's still fighting off\Nthe first wave and can't break away.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I see...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:03:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}The 24 targets appear to have splashed\Ndown in the sea 30 km ahead of us.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Ask the Prometheus to send out\Nsome patrol helicopters.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}They should be arriving in five minutes, sir.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}That was quick thinking.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Thank you.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:16.44,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FF00&\pos(70,134)}COUNT DOWN{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What is that thing?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}An alien robot?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}You've gotta be kidding!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}It looks like it's stopped.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Yeah...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Hey, Minmay!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Be careful, Yot-chan!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What if that thing had stepped on you?!\NGoodness...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Hey!\NLet's go take a look at the robot!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Go?\NGo where?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}The third floor!\NYour room!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Wait!\NI'm coming, too!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Come right back, you hear?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Okay!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}This is patrol helicopter PHP-202.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}We are currently over the ocean.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Roger. Be careful.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}They've opened fire!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Turn back!\NHurry!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}The patrol helicopters have been shot down.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}It looks like they're trying to\Nsurround the island.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}We have to stay alert!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Yes, sir.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Well, well, well.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I must say, it's always a pleasure to\Nbe on this splendid bridge.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Sir.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}So, Global, my friend...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Just when do you plan on\Nlaunching the Macross?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Launching it, sir?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}The ship still hasn't been\Nproperly outfitted.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}We've put a great deal of money into\Nrepairing this spaceship.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}We'd hate to see it destroyed\Nsitting on the ground.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I understand, sir, but...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}That's your response for everything,\Nisn't it Global?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}Say, Kim, are we going into space?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}ARMD-II is still combat-ready; launch\Nand dock with it immediately!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}It sure looks that way.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Why have you just been sitting\Nhere this whole time?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}Oh, no!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}What do you mean, "Oh, no"?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}Up until yesterday, you were so excited\Nabout going up into space!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What can the Macross accomplish by\Nstaying here and not launching?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}Yeah... I was, but...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}But we have reports that{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}the enemy forces have warships even\Nbigger than the Macross, and...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}It's not about size, is it?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}It's about having the ambition\Nto get the job done!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}But, sir...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Or are you telling me, Global,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}that the Macross will be defeated\Nwithout even putting up a fight?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}N...No, sir.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Then launch, why don't you?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Yes, sir.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Very good.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}You just leave the negotiations with\Nthese aliens to us politicians.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}You all do your best, too, all right?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.74,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}In other words, we're just buying time...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}It's huge!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Yot-chan!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}It's moving!\NHey, it's moving!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Its head split open!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Yeah...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}No one's inside?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Strange, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}It's moving again!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What the heck is going on here?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Um, excuse me!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What does this look like to you?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What does it look like?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Well, obviously, it's a big...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Yeah, obviously.\NThat's what I thought.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I don't believe it!\NThe plane turned into a damn robot!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}The plane turned into a robot?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}How is that possible?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}That's what I wanna know!\NJeez...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What?\NBut you're the pilot, aren't you?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Just because I'm a pilot doesn't\Nmean I'm a soldier, you know!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What?!\NThen why are you...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}How can I put this?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}He's a thief!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Yot-chan!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}You little...!\NAnyway, it's gotten pretty banged up...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}But wasn't it expensive?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Er...very.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Hey, buddy!\NHow about gettin' off the road?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I'm tryin' to evacuate to the shelter!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Yes, sir!\NI'll get right to it!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Well,then...bye!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Take care, okay?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Sure.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I sure hope I can get this thing to work...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}All right, here we go!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Look out!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Help!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Yot-chan, are you okay?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Yeah.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Are you all right, miss?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I think so.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}That's a relief!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Gravity control systems 1 through 48,\Nare you showing green?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}No. 4, green.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Roger.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}No. 16, preparations complete.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Roger.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}GH block 24, prepare for launch.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}No. 16, are you clear?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}AF 74 through 140, please complete\Npreparations on the double!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}No.34, are you clear?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}Roger.\NBlock 25, prepare for launch ASAP!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Incoming transmission from\NUN Forces High Command.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Space carriers ARMD-I and ARMD-II\Nhave completed fighter retrieval...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}...and are now proceeding to\Nthe rendezvous point.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Claudia, what's our reactor status?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}We can launch at any time, sir.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Very well.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}All hands, commence liftoff!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}All hands, commence liftoff!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}All hands, commence liftoff!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}All hands, commence liftoff!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}All hands, commence liftoff!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Initiating transfer of main reactor output\Nto gravity control systems.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}T-minus ten seconds to liftoff.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Nine... Eight...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Seven... Six...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Five... Four...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Three... Two...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}One... Zero!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Liftoff!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Good.\NSo far so good...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What in the world is happening?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I don't know, sir!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Captain!\NThe bow!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What is it?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What are those?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}They appear to be the\Ngravity control systems.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}The gravity control systems?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}That's impossible!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Is everyone all right?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Yes, sir.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Kim, Shammy, get me a damage report!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Roger.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What a terrible ship!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}That's what we get for trying to\Nuse salvaged parts, sir.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}That's for sure.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Okay!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Stop, stop!\NStop!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Skull Leader to Gunsight One.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Skull Leader to Gunsight One.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}We've sent the enemy air forces\Nback where they came from.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}We are heading back to the ship.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Roger that, Major.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}How many did you get?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Only ten.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Adequate, I suppose.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, I haven't seen any action in two years!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Anyway, do you know the\Nlocation of the VT-102?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}VT-102 made an emergency landing\Nin the city a while ago.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Really?\NThat's good news!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Is there something the matter\Nwith the VT-102?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I'll explain later.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}That's it, over and out!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Skull Leader to all units.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}You guys head back to the Prometheus.\NI've gotta make a quick stop first.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Roger.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}Roger.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Okay, now...\NWhere'd that idiot get to?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Over there, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}VT-102, come in.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}102! Hikaru!\NDo you read me?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Sempai!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}You don't give up, do you?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Yeah. Sorry to disappoint you,\Nbut I'm still alive.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Wow, that's some change!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}It turned into a robot!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}It sure did...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Well, Hikaru?\NHow was your first time getting shot down?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Not very good, obviously!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}And what's with these fighter planes\Nturning into robots?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I can't really get into that right now.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What, is it some military secret?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Exactly.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}So why don't you join up?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}You're dreaming! And would you\Nplease do something about this?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Calm down.\NI'll have you fixed up in five minutes.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}All right, that should do it.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Put both feet on the pedals\Nand press slowly.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Okay. Like this?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Good job.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Is it fixed?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Yes.\NThank you for your help.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Minmay, let's go.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Okay!\NWell, see you!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Sure thing.\NBe careful!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Auntie, wait!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}It looks like we're the last ones.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Right.\NWe'd better hurry up and evacuate.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Hey, Hikaru!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}You take after me more and more\Nevery day! You dog!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}It's not like that at all!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Hey, take it easy!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Jeez...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Reguld platoons have made landfall.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Understood.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}All ships, prepare for barrage.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Provide support for ground units.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Roger!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Well, I guess we should get going, too.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}That's easy for you to say.\NI don't know how to pilot a robot!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Oh, right. Okay, change to Gerwalk mode.\NIt's the lever marked "G" on your left.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}This one?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}The controls for this aren't that much\Ndifferent from a fighter plane's.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Really?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}You okay?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Oh, no!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I left something at the house, Auntie!\NI'm going to go back for it!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}No, Minmay.\NIt's too dangerous.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I'll be fine.\NI'll be right back!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Be careful!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}All ships have completed\Npreparations for barrage!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Good. Begin firing, and have the\NReguld platoons move in.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Capture the enemy battleship!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What was that?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I'm not sure, but I think it\Nwas an enemy attack.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}It looks like the city got hit\Npretty hard, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I'm worried about that girl and her family.\NWanna go take a look?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Okay.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Details on the attack?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}It came from orbit!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}They're attacking us from above?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Captain! Multiple enemy units are\Nclosing in. It's a ground assault!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Gunsight One to all Valkyrie units.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Assume B-mode and destroy\Nenemy ground units!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Brown Squadron, roger!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Cerulean Squadron, roger!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Hikaru!\NTake care of the girl!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}How am I supposed to do that?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Aah, quit whining!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I'll draw off the enemy fire!\NC'mon, move it!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Grab on!\NHurry!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Hey, you're that guy.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Just do it!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}All right...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Get out of here!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Everything all right?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I guess I'm okay.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Not you!\NThe girl!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}She's okay... For the\Ntime being.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Good! I don't care if YOU die,\Njust be sure that she stays safe.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}So that's how it is, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Yup, that's how it is.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Well, see you later.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Oh no, I forgot that this plane\Nis a two-seater!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Are you all right?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Y...Yes.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Thank you.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Whew, that's a relief!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Huh? Oh, no!\NMy hair's a mess!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Which is more important,\Nyour hair or your life?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}My hair, of course!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I knew it!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}It... It can't be!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}So now you know.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}The Battroids were built to\Nfight these giants.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}That's impossible!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Still, I had no idea they looked\Njust like humans.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Rocket engines are standing by\Nand ready to begin liftoff.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Civilian evacuation status?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}All the island's civilians have\Nevacuated to the shelters.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Very well. Fire main rockets.\NTake us up at once!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.25,0:22:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I wonder if it will work this time.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Don't worry.\NThis propulsion system was made on Earth.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Let's go!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.19,0:22:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Yes, sir!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Skull Leader, provide escort for the Macross.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Roger that.\NLet's go, Hikaru!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}What's the matter, Hikaru?\NTake off!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.06,0:23:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Are you coming or not?!\NHikaru!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:18.14,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Through the sudden appearance\Nof the giant alien,...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:21.23,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}and the sight of it being killed\Nbefore his very eyes,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.42,0:23:23.59,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Hikaru came to know the\Nmeaning of true terror.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:30.15,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Major Focker's calls went unheard\Nas Hikaru sat, lost in thought.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.49,0:23:39.03,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Faced with the overwhelming power\Nof the enemy forces,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.42,0:23:42.35,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Captain Global decides to\Nexecute a space fold.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:46.86,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}However, neither the enemy forces\Nnor Captain Global{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:51.56,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}could have known the effects that\Nthis first fold would have.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.39,0:23:55.31,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}{\c&H00FFFF&}The Macross will find itself facing an\Naltogether new kind of battle.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.06,0:23:58.90,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.84,0:24:01.27,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}"SPACE FOLD"{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.94,0:24:23.62,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&}I won't follow it anymore,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.88,0:24:30.29,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&}the shadow you cast as you run away{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:36.78,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&}We all keep running until the end,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.16,0:24:44.64,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&}but we still can't see the goal{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.92,0:24:51.39,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&}What awaits us after today?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.46,0:24:57.36,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&}What awaits us beyond tomorrow?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.50,0:25:04.77,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&}Even now, I keep running toward{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.02,0:25:16.08,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&}the light that shines so far away{\b0}
